casebody.data:
WADE ROSEBORO v. COMMISSIONER OF CORRECTION (AC 24575)

Lavery, C. J., and Foti and West, Js.

Submitted on briefs October 27 officially released November 16, 2004 *902Per Curiam.

The habeas court did not abuse its discretion in denying the petition for certification to appeal from the dismissal of the habeas petition.

The appeal is dismissed.
